text: Matanuska-Susitna Borough (often referred to as the Mat-Su Borough) is a borough in the U.S. state of Alaska. As of the 2020 census, the population was 107,801. The borough seat is Palmer, and largest city is Wasilla. == References == ==Other websites== * Official government website Category:Alaska boroughs Category:1960s establishments in Alaska Category:1964 establishments in the United States
